===Etymology===
Old English ''[[lengþu]]''

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-length.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The [[measurement]] of [[distance]] along the longest [[dimension]] of an object.
# (''Horse racing'') The length of a [[horse]], used to indicate the [[distance]] between horses at the end of a [[race]].
#{{mathematics}} See [[magnitude]].
#{{cricket}} the [[distance]] down the [[pitch]] that the ball [[bounce]]s on its way to the [[batsman]]

